"Overall: Super well balanced, and really easy drinking. If this were cheap and in 6 packs I would go through a lot of this. Really impressive."
"A very slight grape like quality with this beer. Big roasted chocolate and coffee notes. Light in flavor. Slight hop character. Overall very easy to drink, and it gets better as it warms. Little lacing and head. A nice sweetness. Slight rye but not big."
